sx-a11y/click-events-have-key-events","Visible, non-interactive elements with click handlers must have at least one keyboard listener.","jsx-a11y/no-static-element-interactions","Avoid non-native interactive elements. If using native HTML is not possible, add an appropriate role and support for tabbing, mouse, keyboard, and touch inputs to an interactive content element.",{"range":"1207","text":"1198"},{"range":"1208","text":"1198"},{"range":"1209","text":"1198"},{"range":"1210","text":"1198"},"@typescript-eslint/no-shadow","'prev' is already declared in the upper scope on line 54 column 9.","noShadow",{"range":"1211","text":"1198"},{"range":"1212","text":"1198"},{"range":"1213","text":"1198"},{"range":"1214","text":"1198"},{"range":"1215","text":"1198"},{"range":"1216","text":"1198"},{"range":"1217","text":"1198"},"react/no-unstable-nested-components","Do not define components during render. React will see a new component type on every render and destroy the entire subtree’s DOM nodes and state (https://reactjs.org/docs/reconciliation.html#elements-of-different-types). Instead, move this component definition out of the parent component “BookDetailPage” and pass data as props.",{"range":"1218","text":"1219"},{"range":"1220","text":"1198"},{"range":"1221","text":"1198"},{"range":"1222","text":"1198"},{"range":"1223","text":"1198"},{"range":"1224","text":"1198"},{"range":"1225","text":"1198"},{"range":"1226","text":"1198"},{"range":"1227","text":"1198"},{"range":"1228","text":"1198"},{"range":"1229","text":"1198"},{"range":"1230","text":"1198"},{"range":"1231","text":"1198"},{"range":"1232","text":"1198"},{"range":"1233","text":"1198"},{"range":"1234","text":"1198"},{"range":"1235","text":"1198"},{"range":"1236","text":"1198"},{"range":"1237","text":"1198"},{"range":"1238","text":"1198"},{"range":"1239","text":"1198"},{"range":"1240","text":"1198"},{"range":"1241","text":"1198"},{"range":"1242","text":"1198"},{"range":"1243","text":"1198"},{"range":"1244","text":"1198